divs: Sighting DetailsSighting Report: It started at 9:05. it was in the east. there was cloud coverage.We thought it was a car reflectingonto the clouds. Then it repeated the formation for an hour.It headed south then turned east. then we noticed a bright light in the clouds. the lights disapeered. My companions were Mark VanUnen, Kevin Hunt, and Morgan Fahrnow (who spotted the unusual nocturnal light.)
